===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], there were 86 people, 39 households, and 26 families residing in the city. The [[population density]] was 87.1 inhabitants per square mile (33.6/km<sup>2</sup>). There were 48 housing units at an average density of 48.6 per square mile (18.8/km<sup>2</sup>).<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A09100&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

The median age in the city was 46.5 years. 23.3% of residents were under the age of 20; 3.5% were between the ages of 20 and 24; 19.8% were from 25 to 44; 25.6% were from 45 to 64; and 27.9% were 65 years of age or older. 20.9% of residents were under the age of 18. For every 100 females there were 109.8 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over there were 126.7 males age 18 and over.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

All residents lived in rural areas.<ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A09100&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

Of the 39 households, 25.6% had children under the age of 18 living with them, 38.5% were [[Marriage|married-couple households]], 7.7% were cohabitating-couple households, 20.5% had a female householder with no spouse or partner present, and 33.3% had a male householder with no spouse or partner present. 33.3% of all households were non-families. 28.2% of all households were made up of individuals, and 5.1% had someone living alone who was 65 years of age or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

Of the 48 housing units, 18.8% were vacant. The homeowner vacancy rate was 0.0% and the rental vacancy rate was 12.5%.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

